061 | 六月四日：双胞胎的八字能量差异

https://fenxiao.xiaoe-tech.com/#/try_page/1/app8XNcsEhV8126/v_5cf6212fc4350_WNCMMKL4

<section style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;"><section style="max-width: 100%;"><section style="max-width: 100%;"><section style="max-width: 100%;"><section style="max-width: 100%; line-height: 25.6px;"><section style="margin: 5px auto; max-width: 100%; border-width: 0px; border-style: none;"><section style="color: inherit; max-width: 100%; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; height: 25px;"><section style="max-width: 100%; height: 25px; width: 50px; float: left; border-top: 2px solid rgb(33, 33, 34); border-right-color: rgb(33, 33, 34); border-bottom-color: rgb(33, 33, 34); border-left: 2px solid rgb(33, 33, 34); color: inherit;"></section><section style="display: inline-block; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(33, 33, 34); clear: both; border-color: rgb(33, 33, 34);"></section></section><p class="p1" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both;"><span style="color: rgb(76, 76, 76); font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.544px;">世界上最高最大的学问莫过于象，</span><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both;"><br/></p><section style="padding-right: 6px; padding-left: 6px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(76, 76, 76); font-size: 15px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">最高最大的象莫过于卦象。</span></section><p style="margin: -0.8em 8px; padding: 0.8em; clear: both; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><section style="padding-right: 6px; padding-left: 6px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(76, 76, 76); font-size: 15px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">八卦和六十四卦象是宇宙信息，</span></section><p style="margin: -0.8em 8px; padding: 0.8em; clear: both; max-width: 100%; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><br/></p><section style="padding-right: 6px; padding-left: 6px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="max-width: 100%; color: rgb(76, 76, 76); font-size: 15px; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">是最大的数据库。</span></section><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both;"><br/></p><section style="margin: -0.8em 0.3em; padding: 0.8em; max-width: 100%;"><p style="margin: 0px 8px; clear: both; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: right;"><span style="color: rgb(76, 76, 76); font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.544px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;—— 张树旗老师</span><span style="color: rgb(76, 76, 76); font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.544px;"></span><br/></p></section><section style="color: inherit; max-width: 100%; line-height: 25.6px; font-family: 微软雅黑; height: 25px;"><section style="max-width: 100%; height: 25px; width: 50px; float: right; border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(33, 33, 34); border-top-color: rgb(33, 33, 34); border-right: 2px solid rgb(33, 33, 34); border-left-color: rgb(33, 33, 34); color: inherit;"></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: left; white-space: normal;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5;"></span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: left; white-space: normal;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5;"><br/></span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;"><span style="color: rgb(192, 0, 0); font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.5;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(192, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5;">课程亮点</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal;"><span style="color: rgb(192, 0, 0); font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.5;"><strong><span style="color: rgb(192, 0, 0); line-height: 1.5;"><br/></span></strong></span></p><p><br/></p><section style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;"><section style="letter-spacing: 1px; border-width: 0px; border-style: none; border-color: initial;"><section style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px;"><section style="padding: 10px; background-color: rgb(239, 239, 239);"><section><p style="margin: 0px 8px; clear: both; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(106, 106, 90); letter-spacing: 0.544px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; clear: both; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(106, 106, 90);"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.544px;">《易经》六十四卦组合在一起，它的时空信息是可以互动的，这是一套完整的符号系统</span>，如此简单，为什么几千年来人们都学不懂呢？</span><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; clear: both; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(106, 106, 90);"></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; clear: both; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(106, 106, 90);">张树旗老师总结了四句话：</span><strong><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(90, 90, 90);"></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; clear: both; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><strong><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(90, 90, 90);"><br/></span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; clear: both; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);">自古学易入误区，不知卦象解传语，</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; clear: both; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);">伏羲生在文字前，舍本求末乱痴迷。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; clear: both; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="color: rgb(90, 90, 90);">具体说来《易经》包含</span><span style="color: rgb(123, 12, 0);">卦象</span><span style="color: rgb(90, 90, 90);">和</span><span style="color: rgb(123, 12, 0);">释象</span><span style="color: rgb(90, 90, 90);">（即文字）两部分,卦象是本，释象是末。</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; clear: both; letter-spacing: 0.544px; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(90, 90, 90); font-size: 15px;">张树旗老师正是从最基础的卦象入手，用形象生动的语言，以自然万物作类比，追本溯源，把《易经》给讲活了。</span><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(90, 90, 90);"></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; letter-spacing: 0.544px;"><br/></p></section></section><section style="margin-top: -4px; font-size: 16px; width: 556px; transform: rotate(0deg);"><section style="width: 50px; height: 4px; background-color: rgb(117, 117, 118); color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></section></section></section></section><p class="" style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p></section><p><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; line-height: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(90, 90, 90); font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.544px;"></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; line-height: 2em;"><strong><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);">问渠哪得清如许，为有源头活水来。</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; line-height: 2em;"><strong><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);">《易经》正是中华文化的源头活水。</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; line-height: 2em;"><strong><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);">那么，如何走进《易经》的世界呢？</span></strong><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);"></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; line-height: 2em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; line-height: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(90, 90, 90);">辛庄师范特别邀请</span><strong><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);">张树旗</span><span style="font-size: 15px; color: rgb(90, 90, 90);">老师</span></strong></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; line-height: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(90, 90, 90); font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.544px;">讲述</span><strong style="color: rgb(90, 90, 90); font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.544px;">《365每日易经》</strong><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; line-height: 2em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; line-height: 2em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);">4月5日</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(90, 90, 90);">开始，</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; line-height: 2em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(90, 90, 90);">每日早上</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.544px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(123, 12, 0);">6:30</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.544px; color: rgb(90, 90, 90); font-size: 15px;">张树旗老师带大家</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; line-height: 2em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.544px; color: rgb(90, 90, 90); font-size: 15px;">探寻中华文化的源头，</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 8px; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: center; white-space: normal; line-height: 2em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.544px; color: rgb(90, 90, 90); font-size: 15px;">识象、知数、明位、通变</span></p><p style="line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><strong><br/></strong></p><p style="line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;"><strong><br/></strong></p><p style="line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"><strong><span style="color: rgb(192, 0, 0); font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.5;">讲师介绍</span></strong></span><br/></p><p style="line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;"><strong><br/></strong></p><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app6ovCb8Zj3569/image/ueditor/8377000_1555481578.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="1.jpg" width="181" height="272" style="width: 181px; height: 271.741px;"/></p><p style="white-space: normal; border: 0px; margin-top: 0.63em; margin-bottom: 1.8em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; caret-color: rgb(25, 25, 25); color: rgb(25, 25, 25); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><strong><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px;">张树旗老师</span></strong></span></p><p style="white-space: normal; border: 0px; margin-top: 0.63em; margin-bottom: 1.8em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; caret-color: rgb(25, 25, 25); color: rgb(25, 25, 25); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><strong><span style="text-align: left; text-indent: 2em;">幼</span></strong><span style="text-align: left; text-indent: 2em;">承家学，张氏梅花风水学派第五代传人，唯象解易法创研人。境内外多所高校的特聘教授，境内外多家政府及企事业单位的高级顾问。2008年5月出版《中国城市风水一点通（省会篇）》，乃中国第一部全面写中国城市风水的著作。2011年出版40万字的演易著作《易论天下》，开辟了解析《易经》的新途径和新方法，2014年出版《三字易经》。</span></span></p><p style="white-space: normal; border: 0px; margin-top: 0.63em; margin-bottom: 1.8em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; caret-color: rgb(25, 25, 25); color: rgb(25, 25, 25); font-family: &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em;"><span style="border: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><strong>张</strong>树旗先生于2002年开创了<strong>时空风水学派</strong>，并运用其理论做案例，成功率92.6%。所谓时空风水学派，就是以空间和时间的变化为研究对象，以时空对人产生的感应为研究重点，以静态和动态两种形态为研究参数，重在实战，面向大众的一个新的风水学派。</span></p><p style="white-space: normal; border: 0px; margin-top: 0.63em; margin-bottom: 1.8em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; caret-color: rgb(25, 25, 25); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="color:#c00000"><span style="font-size: 17px;"><strong>适合人群</strong></span></span></p><p style="white-space: normal; border: 0px; margin-top: 0.63em; margin-bottom: 1.8em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; caret-color: rgb(25, 25, 25); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 0em;"><span style="color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px; text-indent: 2em;">◐ </span><span style="color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px; text-indent: 2em;">广大的《易经》爱好者；</span><br/></p><p style="white-space: normal; border: 0px; margin-top: 0.63em; margin-bottom: 1.8em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; caret-color: rgb(25, 25, 25); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 0em;"><span style="color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 15px; text-indent: 2em;">◐ <span style="color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; text-indent: 30px; caret-color: rgb(25, 25, 25);">零基础，但对《易经》感兴趣的朋友</span></span></p><p style="white-space: normal; border: 0px; margin-top: 0.63em; margin-bottom: 1.8em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; caret-color: rgb(25, 25, 25); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"></p><p style="white-space: normal; border: 0px; margin-top: 0.63em; margin-bottom: 1.8em; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; caret-color: rgb(25, 25, 25); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Arial, 微软雅黑, 宋体, simsun, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><strong style="text-align: center; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);">课程大纲</span></strong></p><p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><strong>一、总体思路</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">通过易象、干支象与万物之象的综合解读，</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">缕清现象之间的内在联系，</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">找到中国几千年的文化本源，正本清源。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">通过365天的学习，了解到易经在生活的应用。</span></p><p><br/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><strong>二、 主要内容</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">河图洛书揭密</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><strong>八卦六十四卦</strong>符号系统的真正内涵</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><strong>太极图</strong>与宇宙运行秩序的关系</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><strong>先、后天</strong><strong>太极八卦图</strong>的功用</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><strong>二十四节气</strong>的发现与定位</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><strong>七十二候</strong>解读</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><strong>天干地支</strong>的缘起以及蕴藏的宇宙能量</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">解读<strong>运、气、命</strong>和他们之间的必然联系</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><strong>环境风水学</strong>的起源以及在生活中的运用</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">......</span></p><p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><br/></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"></span></p><p style="text-indent: 34px; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><font color="#c00000"><span style="font-size: 17px; caret-color: rgb(25, 25, 25);"><b>您将获得</b></span></font></p><p style="text-indent: 34px; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.5em;"><font color="#c00000"><span style="font-size: 17px; caret-color: rgb(25, 25, 25); color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><br/></span></font></p><p style="text-indent: 34px; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><font color="#c00000"><span style="font-size: 17px; caret-color: rgb(25, 25, 25); color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">每天<span style="font-size: 17px; caret-color: rgb(25, 25, 25); color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">一集，</span></span></font></p><p style="text-indent: 34px; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><font color="#c00000"><span style="font-size: 17px; caret-color: rgb(25, 25, 25); color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><span style="font-size: 17px; caret-color: rgb(25, 25, 25); color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">每集10—15分钟，</span></span></font></p><p style="text-indent: 34px; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><font color="#c00000"><span style="font-size: 17px; caret-color: rgb(25, 25, 25); color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><span style="font-size: 17px; caret-color: rgb(25, 25, 25); color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">伴您365天，</span></span></font></p><p style="text-indent: 34px; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><font color="#c00000"><span style="font-size: 17px; caret-color: rgb(25, 25, 25); color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><span style="font-size: 17px; caret-color: rgb(25, 25, 25); color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">跟着张老师，</span></span></font></p><p style="text-indent: 34px; white-space: normal; line-height: 1.5em; text-align: center;"><font color="#c00000"><span style="font-size: 17px; caret-color: rgb(25, 25, 25); color: rgb(89, 89, 89);"><span style="font-size: 17px; caret-color: rgb(25, 25, 25); color: rgb(89, 89, 89);">轻轻松松读懂《易经》</span></span><span style="font-size: 17px; caret-color: rgb(25, 25, 25);"><b><br/></b></span></font></p><p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="white-space: normal; line-height: 1.5em; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.54px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: STZhongsong; caret-color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><span style="color: rgb(249, 110, 87); font-size: 10px;">购买须知：</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.54px; white-space: normal; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: STZhongsong; caret-color: rgb(62, 62, 62);"><span style="color: rgb(249, 110, 87); font-size: 10px;">1.本课程为线上视频课程，一经订阅不可退订、转让；课程购买之后，可永久回看；</span><